      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to speak of. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creases, while the original floor mats look as though they\u2019ve never seen a shoe. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with the precision of a new car. Mechanically, the engine bay is spotless, and the vehicle drives with the tightness and responsiveness of the day it rolled off the assembly line. All original documentation, complete service records, and both sets of keys are included. This is a collector-grade piece for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
