      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered like a member of the family. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come by and take a look!",
