      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. This S54-powered icon features a 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically, this example is beyond reproach: the critical rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul are documented, and the rear subframe has been pro-actively reinforced to ensure chassis integrity. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension geometry is dialed to original specifications with fresh bushings throughout. The exterior retains its deep factory luster, while the interior shows no signs of bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster\u2014a truly turnkey specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
